r:telegram:group:-5168104492","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5168104492","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"updatedAt":1775990629434,"sessionId":"731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":20343,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775990537840,"endedAt":1775990629120,"runtimeMs":91280,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5168104492","lastAccountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can see the full ecosystem. No `qlhv` found in memory. Let me now analyze the prompt and produce the optimization output.\n\nLet me now run the full Phase 0-5 analysis and produce the output.\n\n**Project Detection:**\n- AGENTS.md exists (confirmed via context)\n- No package.json detected (empty dir listing - this is a skills workspace, not a code project)\n- Tech stack: **unknown** вЂ” no code files detected in current workspace\n\n**Intent Detection:**\n- Keywords: \"Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ\", \"bГЎo cГЎo\", \"match database\", \"logic chЖ°a khб»›p\", \"vбєҐn Д‘б»Ѓ\"\n- Category: **Review** + **Research** вЂ” a system audit/evaluation task\n"},{"type":"text","text":"## вљ™пёЏ Prompt Diagnosis\n\n### Prompt gб»‘c:\n> *\"master thб»±c hiб»‡n triб»ѓn khai yГЄu cбє§u Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ, bГЎo cГЎo cho tГґi chi tiбєїt vб»Ѓ hб»‡ thб»‘ng qlhv nГ y xem lГ  cГі match database vб»›i master chЖ°a, cГі phбє§n logic nГ o chЖ°a khб»›p hay cГі nhб»Їng vбєҐn Д‘б»Ѓ gГ¬\"*\n\n---\n\n### Strengths\n- вњ… Mб»Ґc tiГЄu rГµ: Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ hб»‡ thб»‘ng `qlhv` вЂ” so khб»›p DB + logic\n- вњ… CГі yГЄu cбє§u bГЎo cГЎo chi tiбєїt\n\n### Issues\n\n| Issue | Impact | Suggested Fix |\n|-------|--------|---------------|\n| KhГґng chб»‰ rГµ **hб»‡ thб»‘ng qlhv** nбє±m б»џ Д‘Гўu (repo, Д‘Ж°б»ќng dбє«n, project) | Agent khГґng tГ¬m Д‘Ж°б»Јc codebase в†’ trбєЈ lб»ќi sai hoбє·c thб»«a | Cung cбєҐp repo path hoбє·c workspace chб»©a hб»‡ thб»‘ng qlhv |\n| KhГґng chб»‰ rГµ **\"master\"** lГ  ai вЂ” lГ  agent `@master-orchestrator`, mб»™t repo cб»Ґ thб»ѓ, hay branch/commit? | Routing nhбє§m в†’ sai agent | Chб»‰ rГµ agent phб»Ґ trГЎch hoбє·c source of truth |\n| KhГґng cГі **acceptance criteria** вЂ” khi nГ o thГ¬ bГЎo cГЎo Д‘б»§? | Kбєїt quбєЈ mб»џ, khГґng biбєїt dб»«ng б»џ Д‘Гўu | ThГЄm tiГЄu chГ­ Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ cб»Ґ thб»ѓ |\n| KhГґng phГўn biб»‡t **database nГ o vs database nГ o** вЂ” so khб»›p cГЎi gГ¬? | KhГґng rГµ scope so sГЎnh | Liб»‡t kГЄ schema cбє§n so sГЎnh (source DB vs target DB) |\n| KhГґng chб»‰ rГµ **output format** вЂ” bГЎo cГЎo dбєЎng bбєЈng, markdown, issue list? | KhГґng Д‘б»“ng nhбєҐt | Chб»‰ rГµ format: markdown / Confluence / file |\n| KhГґng chб»‰ rГµ **phбєЎm vi logic** вЂ” lГ  tбє§ng nГ o (API, service, repository)? | Kiб»ѓm tra lan man hoбє·c thiбєїu | Giб»›i hбєЎn: chб»‰ logic nghiб»‡p vб»Ґ + database layer |\n\n---\n\n## Recommended Components\n\n| Type | Component | Purpose |\n|------|-----------|---------|\n| Orchestrator | `@master-orchestrator` | Дђiб»Ѓu phб»‘i cross-domain review, giao viб»‡c cho cГЎc agent chuyГЄn biб»‡t |\n| Skill | `@database-schema-designer` | So khб»›p schema, phГЎt hiб»‡n missing/extra fields, FK constraints |\n| Skill | `@senior-backend` | Review logic nghiб»‡p vб»Ґ, API contracts, service layer |\n| Skill | `@coding-standards` | Kiб»ѓm tra naming, patterns, DRY/KISS compliance |\n| Skill | `@senior-security` | PhГЎt hiб»‡n vбєҐn Д‘б»Ѓ bбєЈo mбє­t trong DB access |\n\n---\n\n## Optimized Prompt вЂ” Full Version\n\n```\n## Task: ДђГЎnh giГЎ & BГЎo cГЎo Hб»‡ thб»‘ng QLHV вЂ” So khб»›p Database & Logic\n\n### 1. Ngб»Ї cбєЈnh\n- Hб»‡ thб»‘ng: QLHV (QuбєЈn lГЅ Hб»Ќc viГЄn)\n- Vб»‹ trГ­ codebase: <CHб»€_Rб»њI_ДђЖЇб»њNG_DбєЄN_REPO_QLHV>  в†ђ THAY Bбє°NG PATH THб»°C Tбєѕ\n- Database nguб»“n (source): <TГЉN_DB_QLHV>  в†ђ VD: MongoDB collection \"students\", \"courses\"\n- Database master (target): <TГЉN_DB_MASTER>  в†ђ VD: MongoDB collection \"students\", \"courses\"\n- Tech stack phГЎt hiб»‡n: <AUTO_DETECT_HOбє¶C_CHб»€_Rб»–>\n\n### 2. Mб»Ґc tiГЄu\nSo khб»›p hб»‡ thб»‘ng QLHV vб»›i master, phГЎt hiб»‡n:\n  a) **Database mismatch** вЂ” thiбєїu field, thб»«a field, sai kiб»ѓu dб»Ї liб»‡u, FK orphan\n  b) **Logic misalignment** вЂ” business rules khГґng Д‘б»“ng nhбєҐt giб»Їa service layer vs DB\n  c) **VбєҐn Д‘б»Ѓ tiб»Ѓm бє©n** вЂ” security holes, missing validations, edge cases chЖ°a xб»­ lГЅ\n\n### 3. Workflow thб»±c hiб»‡n\n\n**BЖ°б»›c 1 вЂ” @database-schema-designer**\n  в†’ Dump schema cб»§a cбєЈ 2 database (source QLHV + master)\n  в†’ So sГЎnh field-by-field, type, constraints, indexes\n  в†’ Output: BбєЈng diff schema (field mб»›i / thiбєїu / sai type)\n\n**BЖ°б»›c 2 вЂ” @senior-backend**\n  в†’ Review logic nghiб»‡p vб»Ґ trong service layer cб»§a QLHV\n  в†’ Kiб»ѓm tra API endpoints: request/response contract cГі match DB schema khГґng\n  в†’ Output: Danh sГЎch logic chЖ°a khб»›p hoбє·c thiбєїu validation\n\n**BЖ°б»›c 3 вЂ” @senior-security**\n  в†’ Kiб»ѓm tra truy vбєҐn DB: cГі SQL/NoSQL injection khГґng?\n  в†’ Kiб»ѓm tra quyб»Ѓn truy cбє­p, auth enforcement\n  в†’ Output: Danh sГЎch rб»§i ro bбєЈo mбє­t (nбєїu cГі)\n\n**BЖ°б»›c 4 вЂ” @master-orchestrator**\n  в†’ Tб»•ng hб»Јp kбєїt quбєЈ tб»« BЖ°б»›c 1вЂ“3\n  в†’ PhГўn loбєЎi: рџ”ґ Critical / рџџЎ Warning / рџџў OK\n\n### 4. Output format (bбєЇt buб»™c)\n\n#### 4.1 Database Diff Table\n| Schema | Collection/Table | Field | Type (QLHV) | Type (Master) | Status |\n|--------|-----------------|-------|-------------|---------------|--------|\n\n#### 4.2 Logic Issues List\n| # | Module | Issue | Severity | Recommendation |\n|---|--------|-------|----------|----------------|\n\n#### 4.3 Security Issues List\n| # | Endpoint/Function | Issue | CVSS-like | Fix |\n\n#### 4.4 Summary\n- Tб»•ng sб»‘ mismatch: X\n- Tб»•ng sб»‘ logic issue: Y\n- Tб»•ng sб»‘ security issue: Z\n- вњ… CГі thб»ѓ proceed hay вќЊ Cбє§n fix trЖ°б»›c\n\n### 5. RГ ng buб»™c\n- KhГґng sб»­a code вЂ” chб»‰ Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ vГ  bГЎo cГЎo\n- KhГґng modify database production\n- Nбєїu repo khГґng tГ¬m thбєҐy в†’ bГЎo lб»—i ngay vГ  hб»Џi lбєЎi path\n\n### 6. Deliverable\n- BГЎo cГЎo hoГ n chб»‰nh dбєЎng Markdown\n- ДђДѓng lГЄn Confluence page nбєїu cГі QLHV workspace\n\n```\n\n---\n\n## Optimized Prompt вЂ” Quick Version\n\n| Intent | Quick Pattern |\n|--------|--------------|\n| Review | `@master-orchestrator вЂ” Д‘ГЎnh giГЎ hб»‡ thб»‘ng QLHV. So khб»›p DB + logic vs master. BГЎo cГЎo table format: diff schema / logic issues / security. KhГґng sб»­a, chб»‰ report.` |\n\n---\n\n## Enhancement Rationale\n\n| Enhancement | Reason |\n|-------------|--------|\n| Chб»‰ rГµ repo path + collection/table | Agent biбєїt Д‘Гўu lГ  source Д‘б»ѓ review вЂ” trГЎnh hallucinate |\n| PhГўn tГЎch BЖ°б»›c 1вЂ“3 theo skill chuyГЄn biб»‡t | ДђбєЈm bбєЈo mб»—i gГіc nhГ¬n Д‘Ж°б»Јc expert xб»­ lГЅ (DB в‰  logic в‰  security) |\n| Output table format bбєЇt buб»™c | Lead nhбє­n Д‘Ж°б»Јc artifact Д‘б»“ng nhбєҐt, khГґng phбєЈi text tб»± do |\n| PhГўn loбєЎi severity (Critical/Warning/OK) | Lead cГі thб»ѓ prioritize action ngay |\n| KhГґng sб»­a, chб»‰ report | ДђбєЈm bбєЈo agent khГґng tб»± ГЅ thay Д‘б»•i production вЂ” Д‘Гєng scope review |\n\n---\n\n> вљ пёЏ **Missing Info cбє§n bбєЎn cung cбєҐp thГЄm:**\n> 1. **Repo/workspace chб»©a hб»‡ thб»‘ng QLHV** nбє±m б»џ Д‘Гўu?\n> 2. **TГЄn database + collection/table** cбє§n so khб»›p lГ  gГ¬?\n> 3. **Branch/commit master** nГ o lГ  source of truth?\n> 4. **Output Д‘Г­ch** вЂ” gб»­i б»џ Д‘Гўu (Telegram/Confluence/file)?\n> 5. **Confluence space** cГі sбєµn cho QLHV khГґng?\n\nCung cбєҐp thГЄm thГґng tin trГЄn в†’ prompt sбєµn sГ ng paste vГ o agent Д‘б»ѓ thб»±c thi ngay."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":298,"output":2220,"totalTokens":22563,"cacheRead":15219,"cacheWrite":4826,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775990590009,"responseId":"062aaa3ea767173804f105306e5622f6","__openclaw":{"id":"7a8098b4","seq":8}}]},{"key":"agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914-87cc-4bdd-9ee9-20aa3e6473e1","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775990263239,"sessionId":"f3fea8c0-f2eb-474e-9c08-b41766f765ad","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"status":"failed","startedAt":1775990261918,"endedAt":1775990286627,"runtimeMs":24709,"thinkingLevel":"medium","lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/f3fea8c0-f2eb-474e-9c08-b41766f765ad.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:prompt-optimizer:telegram:slash:6053576134","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775990178347,"sessionId":"0d74c438-5460-4bbd-824a-3bdd04655170","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/0d74c438-5460-4bbd-824a-3bdd04655170.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:security-reviewer:subagent:6739034d-567f-4c51-8557-f54f81ff565a","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:security","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982753509,"sessionId":"e0e07a8e-f0f4-4d34-8038-1a225b7374b9","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":56248,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981729596,"endedAt":1775982220900,"runtimeMs":289559,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/security-reviewer/sessions/e0e07a8e-f0f4-4d34-8038-1a225b7374b9.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The security audit report has been written. Let me provide a summary of what I accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"**Security audit complete.** Report written to `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews/security.md`.\n\n## Summary of Findings\n\n**6 Critical vulnerabilities** identified:\n1. **Unauthenticated `/device` endpoint** вЂ” attendance records can be injected by anyone, no machine key enforced\n2. **IDOR in `/niko-wallets/:id`** вЂ” any user's wallet balance readable by any authenticated user\n3. **IDOR in `/employees/:id`** вЂ” `verifyAdminOrOwner` not applied to the route\n4. **IDOR in `/leave-requests/:id`** вЂ” leave data readable without ownership check\n5. **Hardcoded department bypass** вЂ” users in a specific department code get silent admin access (`author.middleware.ts`)\n6. **Swagger `/docs` unauthenticated** вЂ” full API surface exposed to anyone\n\n**5 High risks** including missing rate limiting on login, default `123456` password fallback, refresh token cookie always `secure: false`, and inconsistent token version checking in the auth flow.\n\n**9 Medium risks** covering missing Helmet headers, regex injection via unsanitized query params, missing manager checks on leave approvals, permissive CORS defaults, and no audit logging for sensitive operations.\n\n**Priority fix list** with 16 items ranked P1в†’P4 with estimated fix times included for the dev team."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"inp